g(t) = \lVert (I + t xx^T)^{-1} \rVert_1 \,, t \geq 0 \,.
 (I + t xx^T)^{-1} = I - \frac{t}{1 + t} xx^T \,. 
 g(t)  = n + \alpha \frac{t}{1 + t} \,, 
 \alpha  = -1 + \sum_{i \neq j} \lvert x_i \rvert \lvert x_j \rvert = -2 + \sum_{ij} \lvert x_i \rvert \lvert x_j \rvert = \lvert x \rvert_1^2 - 2 \,. 
